    Class
    Description
    CaloriesFilter
    When sent to DeliveryService::filterMenu(Predicate[]) as one of the elements of the array of Predicates, this filter will select only the MenuItems which more calories the minCalories and fewer calories them maxCalories;
    FatFilter
    When sent to DeliveryService::filterMenu(Predicate[]) as one of the elements of the array of Predicates, this filter will select only the MenuItems which have at the fat range between the min and max value.
    KeyWordsFilter
    When sent to DeliveryService::filterMenu(Predicate[]) as one of the elements of the array of Predicates, this filter will select only the MenuItems which have at least one of the keywords in their title.
    PriceFilter
    When sent to DeliveryService::filterMenu(Predicate[]) as one of the elements of the array of Predicates, this filter will select only the MenuItems which have at the price range between the min and max value.
    ProteinFilter
    When sent to DeliveryService::filterMenu(Predicate[]) as one of the elements of the array of Predicates, this filter will select only the MenuItems which have at the protein range between the min and max value.
    RatingFilter
    When sent to DeliveryService::filterMenu(Predicate[]) as one of the elements of the array of Predicates, this filter will select only the MenuItems which have at the rating range between the min and max value.
    SodiumFilter
    When sent to DeliveryService::filterMenu(Predicate[]) as one of the elements of the array of Predicates, this filter will select only the MenuItems which have at the sodium range between the min and max value.
